{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1086,"text":"About 75 years ago,"},{"time":2776,"text":"my grandfather, a young man,"},{"time":5335,"text":"walked into a tent"},{"time":7246,"text":"that was converted into a"},{"time":8743,"text":"movie theater like that,"},{"time":10454,"text":"and he fell hopelessly in love"},{"time":12654,"text":"with the woman he saw on the"},{"time":13983,"text":"silver screen: none other than Mae West,"},{"time":17312,"text":"the heartthrob of the '30s,"},{"time":19227,"text":"and he could never forget her."},{"time":21267,"text":"In fact, when he had his daughter"},{"time":23187,"text":"many years later, he wanted to"},{"time":25379,"text":"name her after Mae West,"},{"time":26795,"text":"but can you imagine an Indian"},{"time":28379,"text":"child name Mae West?"},{"time":29915,"text":"The Indian family said, no way!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31601,"text":"So when my twin brother Kaesava"},{"time":34539,"text":"was born, he decided to tinker"},{"time":37049,"text":"with the spelling of Keshava's name."},{"time":38764,"text":"He said, if Mae West can be M-A-E,"},{"time":42475,"text":"why can't Keshava be K-A-E?"},{"time":46011,"text":"So he changed Kaesava's spelling."},{"time":48251,"text":"Now Kaesava had a baby boy"},{"time":50322,"text":"called Rehan a couple of weeks ago."},{"time":52522,"text":"He decided to spell, or, rather,"},{"time":54753,"text":"misspell Raehan with an A-E."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56833,"text":"You know, my grandfather died"},{"time":58968,"text":"many years ago when I was"},{"time":60328,"text":"little, but his love for Mae"},{"time":62169,"text":"West lives on as a misspelling"},{"time":64640,"text":"in the DNA of his progeny."},{"time":66416,"text":"That for me is successful legacy. (Laughs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":69560,"text":"You know, as for me,"},{"time":71202,"text":"my wife and I have our own"},{"time":72429,"text":"crazy legacy project."},{"time":74037,"text":"We actually sit every few years,"},{"time":76229,"text":"argue, disagree, fight,"},{"time":78602,"text":"and actually come up with our"},{"time":80444,"text":"very own 200-year plan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82460,"text":"Our friends think we're mad."},{"time":84420,"text":"Our parents think we're cuckoo."},{"time":85908,"text":"Because, you know, we both"},{"time":87244,"text":"come from families that really"},{"time":88612,"text":"look up to humility and wisdom,"},{"time":91613,"text":"but we both like to live"},{"time":93244,"text":"larger than life."},{"time":94581,"text":"I believe in the concept of"},{"time":96091,"text":"a Raja Yogi: Be a dude before"},{"time":98852,"text":"you can become an ascetic."},{"time":100165,"text":"This is me being a rock star,"},{"time":101660,"text":"even if it's in my own house."},{"time":103284,"text":"You know?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104548,"text":"So when Netra and I sat down"},{"time":106260,"text":"to make our first plan"},{"time":107716,"text":"10 years ago, we said"},{"time":109700,"text":"we want the focus of this plan"},{"time":111804,"text":"to go way beyond ourselves."},{"time":113620,"text":"What do we mean by beyond ourselves?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":116284,"text":"Well 200 years, we calculated,"},{"time":119309,"text":"is at the end of our direct"},{"time":121484,"text":"contact with the world."},{"time":122652,"text":"There's nobody I'll meet in"},{"time":124011,"text":"my life will ever live beyond"},{"time":126324,"text":"200 years, so we thought"},{"time":128228,"text":"that's a perfect place where"},{"time":129420,"text":"we should situate our plan and"},{"time":131332,"text":"let our imagination take flight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133060,"text":"You know, I never really"},{"time":134604,"text":"believed in legacy. What am I"},{"time":136292,"text":"going to leave behind? I'm an artist."},{"time":138284,"text":"Until I made a cartoon about 9/11."},{"time":141570,"text":"It caused so much trouble for me."},{"time":144218,"text":"I was so upset."},{"time":145634,"text":"You know, a cartoon that was"},{"time":148114,"text":"meant to be a cartoon of the week"},{"time":149778,"text":"ended up staying so much longer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153010,"text":"Now I'm in the business of"},{"time":155164,"text":"creating art that will"},{"time":156841,"text":"definitely even outlive me, and"},{"time":159204,"text":"I think about what I want to"},{"time":160865,"text":"leave behind through those paintings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162905,"text":"You know, the 9/11 cartoon"},{"time":164897,"text":"upset me so much that I decided"},{"time":168193,"text":"I'll never cartoon again."},{"time":169729,"text":"I said, I'm never going to make any"},{"time":170945,"text":"honest public commentary again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172858,"text":"But of course I continued"},{"time":175353,"text":"creating artwork that was honest"},{"time":177289,"text":"and raw, because I forgot about"},{"time":179466,"text":"how people reacted to my work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181684,"text":"You know, sometimes forgetting"},{"time":183258,"text":"is so important to remain idealistic."},{"time":186249,"text":"Perhaps loss of memory is so"},{"time":188986,"text":"crucial for our survival"},{"time":190929,"text":"as human beings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192298,"text":"One of the most important things"},{"time":194153,"text":"in my 200-year plan that Netra"},{"time":196057,"text":"and I write is what to forget"},{"time":198443,"text":"about ourselves."},{"time":199756,"text":"You know, we carry so much"},{"time":201177,"text":"baggage, from our parents,"},{"time":202586,"text":"from our society, from so many"},{"time":204594,"text":"people -- fears, insecurities -- and"},{"time":208338,"text":"our 200-year plan really lists"},{"time":210193,"text":"all our childhood problems that we have to expire."},{"time":213245,"text":"We actually put an expiry date"},{"time":214746,"text":"on all our childhood problems."},{"time":217220,"text":"The latest date I put was,"},{"time":219085,"text":"I said, I am going to expire"},{"time":221846,"text":"my fear of my leftist, feminist"},{"time":224389,"text":"mother-in-law, and this"},{"time":226798,"text":"today is the date! (Laughs)"},{"time":229920,"text":"She's watching. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231511,"text":"Anyway, you know, I really"},{"time":236359,"text":"make decisions all the time"},{"time":238359,"text":"about how I want to remember"},{"time":239944,"text":"myself, and that's the most important"},{"time":243216,"text":"kind of decisions I make."},{"time":244735,"text":"And this directly translates"},{"time":246607,"text":"into my paintings."},{"time":247930,"text":"But like my friends, I can do"},{"time":250072,"text":"that really well on Facebook,"},{"time":251648,"text":"Pinterest, Twitter, Flickr, YouTube."},{"time":253567,"text":"Name it, I'm on it."},{"time":255000,"text":"I've started outsourcing my"},{"time":257079,"text":"memory to the digital world,"},{"time":258672,"text":"you know? But that comes"},{"time":260112,"text":"with a problem."},{"time":261208,"text":"It's so easy to think of"},{"time":262839,"text":"technology as a metaphor"},{"time":264144,"text":"for memory, but our brains"},{"time":266490,"text":"are not perfect storage devices"},{"time":268437,"text":"like technology."},{"time":269236,"text":"We only remember what we"},{"time":270776,"text":"want to. At least I do."},{"time":272031,"text":"And I rather think of our brains"},{"time":274534,"text":"as biased curators of our"},{"time":276933,"text":"memory, you know? And if"},{"time":279773,"text":"technology is not a metaphor for"},{"time":281597,"text":"memory, what is it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":283229,"text":"Netra and I use our technology"},{"time":286245,"text":"as a tool in our 200-year plan"},{"time":288813,"text":"to really curate our digital legacy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292332,"text":"That is a picture of my mother,"},{"time":295349,"text":"and she recently got a Facebook account."},{"time":298102,"text":"You know where this is going."},{"time":299868,"text":"And I've been very supportive"},{"time":301702,"text":"until this picture shows up"},{"time":304085,"text":"on my Facebook page. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305652,"text":"And I actually untagged myself"},{"time":308909,"text":"first, then I picked up the"},{"time":310373,"text":"phone. I said, \"Mom, you will"},{"time":311732,"text":"never put a picture of me"},{"time":312844,"text":"in a bikini ever again.\""},{"time":314133,"text":"And she said, \"Why? You look"},{"time":317061,"text":"so cute, darling.\" I said,"},{"time":319180,"text":"\"You just don't understand.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":320973,"text":"Maybe we are among the first"},{"time":322956,"text":"generation that really understands"},{"time":324277,"text":"this digital curating of ourselves."},{"time":326468,"text":"Maybe we are the first to even"},{"time":328030,"text":"actively record our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330268,"text":"You know, whether you"},{"time":331820,"text":"agree with, you know, legacy"},{"time":333973,"text":"or not, we are actually leaving"},{"time":336116,"text":"behind digital traces all the time."},{"time":338469,"text":"So Netra and I really wanted"},{"time":340524,"text":"to use our 200-year plan"},{"time":341884,"text":"to curate this digital legacy,"},{"time":344061,"text":"and not only digital legacy"},{"time":345900,"text":"but we believe in curating"},{"time":347060,"text":"the legacy of my past"},{"time":348948,"text":"and future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350132,"text":"How, you may ask?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":351965,"text":"Well, when I think of the future,"},{"time":355533,"text":"I never see myself moving forward"},{"time":357725,"text":"in time. I actually see time"},{"time":359757,"text":"moving backward towards me."},{"time":361829,"text":"I can actually visualize"},{"time":363229,"text":"my future approaching."},{"time":364580,"text":"I can dodge what I don't want"},{"time":366693,"text":"and pull in what I want."},{"time":368181,"text":"It's like a video game obstacle"},{"time":369492,"text":"course. And I've gotten better and better"},{"time":371978,"text":"at doing this. Even when I make"},{"time":373811,"text":"a painting, I actually imagine"},{"time":375844,"text":"I'm behind the painting,"},{"time":377875,"text":"it already exists, and"},{"time":379058,"text":"someone's looking at it,"},{"time":380274,"text":"and I see whether they're"},{"time":381364,"text":"feeling it from their gut."},{"time":382985,"text":"Are they feeling it from their"},{"time":384218,"text":"heart, or is it just a cerebral thing?"},{"time":386884,"text":"And it really informs my painting."},{"time":388992,"text":"Even when I do an art show,"},{"time":390183,"text":"I really think about, what should"},{"time":391207,"text":"people walk away with?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":392759,"text":"I remember when I was 19,"},{"time":395695,"text":"I did, I wanted to do my first"},{"time":397832,"text":"art exhibition, and I wanted the"},{"time":401032,"text":"whole world to know about it."},{"time":402439,"text":"I didn't know TED then,"},{"time":403887,"text":"but what I did was I closed"},{"time":405888,"text":"my eyes tight, and I started"},{"time":407656,"text":"dreaming. I could imagine people"},{"time":409928,"text":"coming in, dressed up, looking"},{"time":411471,"text":"beautiful, my paintings with all"},{"time":413504,"text":"the light, and in my visualization"},{"time":416215,"text":"I actually saw a very famous"},{"time":418071,"text":"actress launching my show,"},{"time":420239,"text":"giving credibility to me."},{"time":421736,"text":"And I woke up from my"},{"time":423799,"text":"visualization and I said,"},{"time":425056,"text":"who was that? I couldn't tell"},{"time":426792,"text":"if it was Shabana Azmi or Rekha,"},{"time":429031,"text":"two very famous Indian actresses,"},{"time":431240,"text":"like the Meryl Streeps of India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433087,"text":"As it turned out, next morning"},{"time":435447,"text":"I wrote a letter to both of them,"},{"time":437167,"text":"and Shabana Azmi replied,"},{"time":439120,"text":"and came and launched"},{"time":440887,"text":"my very first show 12 years ago."},{"time":443952,"text":"And what a bang it started"},{"time":446184,"text":"my career with! You know,"},{"time":447984,"text":"when we think of time in this"},{"time":450400,"text":"way, we can curate not only the"},{"time":452719,"text":"future but also the past."},{"time":456236,"text":"This is a picture of my family,"},{"time":458440,"text":"and that is Netra, my wife."},{"time":461063,"text":"She's the co-creator of my"},{"time":462695,"text":"200-year plan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464176,"text":"Netra's a high school history"},{"time":466215,"text":"teacher. I love Netra,"},{"time":468159,"text":"but I hate history."},{"time":469976,"text":"I keep saying, \"Nets, you live"},{"time":471888,"text":"in the past while I'll create"},{"time":473535,"text":"the future, and when I'm done,"},{"time":475536,"text":"you can study about it.\""},{"time":477032,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":478992,"text":"She gave me an indulgent smile,"},{"time":480991,"text":"and as punishment, she said,"},{"time":483128,"text":"\"Tomorrow I'm teaching a class"},{"time":484863,"text":"on Indian history, and you are"},{"time":487024,"text":"sitting in it, and I'm grading you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":488472,"text":"I'm like, \"Oh, God.\" I went."}]},{"cues":[{"time":490815,"text":"I actually went and sat in"},{"time":492119,"text":"on her class. She started by"},{"time":494312,"text":"giving students primary source"},{"time":496607,"text":"documents from India, Pakistan,"},{"time":499222,"text":"from Britain, and I said,"},{"time":501471,"text":"\"Wow.\" Then she asked them to"},{"time":503615,"text":"separate fact from bias."},{"time":505567,"text":"I said, \"Wow,\" again."},{"time":508359,"text":"Then she said, \"Choose your"},{"time":511319,"text":"facts and biases and create an"},{"time":514623,"text":"image of your own story"},{"time":516902,"text":"of dignity.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":518311,"text":"History as an imaging tool?"},{"time":521566,"text":"I was so inspired."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523199,"text":"I went and created my own"},{"time":524559,"text":"version of Indian history."},{"time":526136,"text":"I actually included stories from"},{"time":528023,"text":"my grandmother."},{"time":529045,"text":"She used to work for the"},{"time":530204,"text":"telephone exchange, and she used"},{"time":531772,"text":"to actually overhear conversations"},{"time":532899,"text":"between Nehru and Edwina Mountbatten."},{"time":535068,"text":"And she used to hear all"},{"time":536644,"text":"kinds of things she shouldn't"},{"time":537779,"text":"have heard. But, you know,"},{"time":540285,"text":"I include things like that."},{"time":541451,"text":"This is my version of Indian history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544245,"text":"You know, if this"},{"time":548531,"text":"is so, it occurred to me that"},{"time":550645,"text":"maybe, just maybe, the primary"},{"time":552868,"text":"objective of our brains"},{"time":554307,"text":"is to serve our dignity."},{"time":557347,"text":"Go tell Facebook to"},{"time":559355,"text":"figure that out!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":560664,"text":"Netra and I don't write our"},{"time":563284,"text":"200-year plan for someone else"},{"time":565097,"text":"to come and execute it"},{"time":566121,"text":"in 150 years. Imagine receiving"},{"time":568264,"text":"a parcel saying, from the past,"},{"time":570161,"text":"okay now you're supposed to"},{"time":571524,"text":"spend the rest of your life"},{"time":572489,"text":"doing all of this. No."},{"time":573947,"text":"We actually write it only"},{"time":575594,"text":"to set our attitudes right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578084,"text":"You know, I used to believe"},{"time":581924,"text":"that education is the most"},{"time":583324,"text":"important tool to leave"},{"time":584805,"text":"a meaningful legacy."},{"time":586262,"text":"Education is great."},{"time":587786,"text":"It really teaches us who"},{"time":589435,"text":"we are, and helps us"},{"time":590771,"text":"contextualize ourselves"},{"time":592090,"text":"in the world, but it's really"},{"time":594056,"text":"my creativity that's taught me"},{"time":596115,"text":"that I can be much more"},{"time":597892,"text":"than what my education told me I am."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600083,"text":"I'd like to make"},{"time":601537,"text":"the argument that creativity is"},{"time":603867,"text":"the most important tool we have."},{"time":606298,"text":"It lets us create who we are,"},{"time":608484,"text":"and curate what is to come."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610395,"text":"I like to think -- Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613635,"text":"I like to think of myself"},{"time":615210,"text":"as a storyteller, where my past"},{"time":617546,"text":"and my future are only stories,"},{"time":620610,"text":"my stories, waiting to be told"},{"time":622899,"text":"and retold. I hope all of you"},{"time":625514,"text":"one day get a chance to"},{"time":627458,"text":"share and write your own"},{"time":629285,"text":"200-year story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630650,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631715,"text":"Shukran! (Applause)"}]}]}